com.tomscz.afswinx.component.abstraction

Interface AFSwinxInteraction

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AFSwinxForm, AFSwinxTable, AFSwinxTopLevelComponent

    public interface AFSwinxInteraction
    This interface specify operation which should implement all afswinx components which contains another components. These components are known as AFSwinxTopLevelComponent. The reason is that components should provide user getting and posting data.
    Since:
    1.0.0.
    Author:
    Martin Tomasek (martin@toms-cz.com)
